Name: Acta Baltica historiae et philosophiae scientiarum
Description:
Acta Baltica Historiae et Philosophiae Scientiarum sees its mission in offering
publishing opportunities for Baltic and non-Baltic scholars in the field of the history
and philosophy of natural and social sciences (including legal studies) to promote
and further international cooperation between scholars of different countries in this field.

The journal is indexed in SCOPUS, CEEOL, EBSCO, ERIH Plus, and DOAJ online databases.

The journal does not have article processing and article submission charges. 
ABHPS is a double blind peer-reviewed research journal.

Responsibility: Baltic Association of the History and Philosophy of Science

Language: English
